Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.45,0:01:34.08,Default,[01;42],0000,0000,0000,,{Act 2: Pretty Voice Attack!}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.66,0:23:39.58,Default,Sign[23;47],0000,0000,0000,,{Act 3: Goddess of the school}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.64,0:01:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.31,0:02:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.48,0:02:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I getting nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.66,0:02:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, I'm too dragged into her pace.{edit? pace, rhythim}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.20,0:02:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go all out-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.59,0:02:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.59,0:02:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It broke...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.37,0:02:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I stepped on it when I was half-asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.68,0:02:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This stick is weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.82,0:02:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin, go buy me a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.86,0:02:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.95,0:02:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want a tougher one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.22,0:02:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One that can withstand an elephant's stomp.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.30,0:02:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go find a stick which isn't so unlucky. {from  inu mo arukeba bou ni ataru - (If you are too forward, you are likely to meet with disaster. / Every dog has his day.) this proverb means if you do something more often, you'll meet with more mistakes.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.90,0:02:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday was really embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.00,0:02:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forget that woman's expression. Not in this lifetime!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.77,0:02:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an instant adhesive. {superglue?}The usage instructions are written on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.32,0:02:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember to spread some newspapers, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.85,0:02:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And your breakfast is in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:02:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.71,0:02:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.47,0:03:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sure is busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.45,0:03:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember to place the dishes in the water after eating. {rice hardens if you keep it out to dry, becoming difficult to clean, thus you always have to place it in water after eating}I'm going out for a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.62,0:03:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.15,0:03:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin! Over here, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't they so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't they so what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're so cute! I don't know why, but I feel like crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.10,0:03:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to squeeze them! Hug them! Cuddle them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I woke up to their calls this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were purring so earnestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.20,0:03:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't hear anything though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.28,0:03:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I heard a stray cat just gave birth recently, are these its offsprings?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.60,0:04:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin, I just thought of something!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.50,0:04:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.15,0:04:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard they have a mother. A grey cat with stripes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't kidnap cats, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.79,0:04:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, our house is a rented one, so keeping pets is forbidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.05,0:04:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.37,0:04:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already said no.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to withdraw some money now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep still, okay? Eat your breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Breakfast...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.27,0:04:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least... at least give them some milk!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.82,0:04:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't feed the kittens cow's milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.70,0:04:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your breasts are too small to give any milk, so give up. {tlc: お前の乳飲まそうにも貧乳だから無理だしな}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.85,0:04:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Haw haw haw haw haw"... that's what you're thinking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.75,0:04:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not thinking about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.10,0:04:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.81,0:04:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If a kitten doesn't drink milk for one day, it'll die of dehydration!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just need to check them once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.28,0:04:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to keep them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.46,0:04:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A god? She sure doesn't behave like one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.48,0:05:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I TOLD you to spread some newspapers, didn't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.74,0:05:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't like what you're thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do I explain it... I don't know about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I have split personalities, so this was her fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cook up a better lie next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.82,0:05:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, what's with this perfect adhesion!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now what? It's been quite a while so it's totally glued on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.03,0:05:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cloth hanger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.68,0:05:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no such ornament in a dining table!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.54,0:05:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's acting a bit strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.63,0:05:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Jin okay? It's tough for a boy to be living on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.69,0:05:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He definitely needs a cute childhood friend to support him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang it up yourself!{tlc}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.31,0:06:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why aren't you bothered by me handling it? {err, need edit}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am busy, and it takes the same effort anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.90,0:06:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that I don't feel like doing it. Besides, if I get seen by others...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.72,0:06:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.38,0:06:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one talking to you on the phone yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done for! She's the person that you shouldn't be meeting the most!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.66,0:06:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's Tsugumi, my childhood friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.71,0:06:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father entrusted me to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.48,0:06:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she finds out that I'm cohabiting with a woman I don't know, it's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.72,0:06:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I'm causing trouble for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so late to notice that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been causing me trouble since yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.17,0:06:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'll go explain to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.12,0:06:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do anything unnecessary. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.05,0:07:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi. It's a long story...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.87,0:07:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only knew her yesterday-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.77,0:07:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to explain...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.07,0:07:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.73,0:07:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't mean that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't be interfering in your relationship...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.38,0:07:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you skip school like that, I'm not sure how to answer to your father...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.09,0:07:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.23,0:07:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for my impertinence earlier.{to editor: she's talking in a very polite and refined manner from now on. please edit if needed}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Jin-kun's relative.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.99,0:07:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.60,0:07:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Relative?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Jin-kun's half sibling, born from a different mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.01,0:07:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No way! Nobody told me about that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.01,0:07:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a surprise that you'd be shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.46,0:07:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-kun also came to know of me only yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.43,0:08:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that can't be! You were behaving differently just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the other me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.33,0:08:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.29,0:08:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the family I was raised in, even laughing aloud is prohibited.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.31,0:08:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was strict and insular.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.32,0:08:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The constant pressure caused my personality to split into two.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.01,0:08:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am deeply sorry to have shown you a disgraceful side of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.50,0:08:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! {Missing line added by ck}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.12,0:08:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's the explanation?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't bear to stay in that house anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.98,0:08:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that it is selfish of me, but this is the only place I can go to!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.78,0:08:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I've misunderstood you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.74,0:08:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But won't they come to take you back soon if you stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That family only think of me as a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.89,0:08:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll just pretend that I've simply vanished and not inquire to the police to look for me.{shorten?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:08:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're joking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, that looks very delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.25,0:09:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can stop pretending already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.89,0:09:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you're so articulate, leading her along like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, and I thought you finally understood that the stick situation was not Nagi's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.80,0:09:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi really knows nothing about that stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.99,0:09:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't berate her for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Split personality?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.51,0:09:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really okay to take her in?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.19,0:09:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father is working right now and you can't contact him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.19,0:09:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... but I don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.76,0:09:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to believe such a thing could happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.28,0:09:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's possible, taking your father into account...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.99,0:09:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's talking about you, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.06,0:09:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, I'd like you to keep her situation a secret as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.97,0:10:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She hopes you do so anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just go on telling others about something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's only if nothing happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were entrusted to me, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.12,0:10:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is far enough. Remember to eat the side dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.25,0:10:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Please send my regards to your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.87,0:10:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Omelets... {fried eggs}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are omelets in there, so eat them, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.20,0:10:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.58,0:10:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you at school tomorrow then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.46,0:10:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.21,0:10:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.96,0:10:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use. Looks like I'll have to get some detachment solution. {something to remove the glue?? <- yes Acetone which is sold as super glue remover}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.50,0:10:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, how did it get stuck so cleanly in the middle?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.14,0:10:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That made me laugh my ass off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While I was applying the adhesive, my hand slipped!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.22,0:11:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It made a beautiful half-turn and scored a ten-point landing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.37,0:11:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was magnificent, but I just burst into laughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.91,0:11:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I rolled around laughing for a while after that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.72,0:11:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute... why are {\i1}you{\i0} talking about that incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.93,0:11:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.78,0:11:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've let the cat out of the bag.{tlc, can't hear <- me neither (A part wo...)}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.58,0:11:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You tricked me, you swindler!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.69,0:11:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.78,0:11:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did that out of impulse!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.85,0:11:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't use your polite speech again! Are you a god of misfortune?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, it's gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's horrible, I saw it directly with my eyes!{tlc:やばいよ　モロ見ちゃった <- normally people dont see dead cats too seriously}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.35,0:11:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was there since forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.63,0:11:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's hopeless...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.24,0:11:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the kittens' mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.72,0:11:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I woke up to their calls this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.75,0:11:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long ago was she not around anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This morning? Or even earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.20,0:11:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If a kitten doesn't drink milk for one day, it'll die of dehydration!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.64,0:12:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I had listened to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've dried up, haven't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.07,0:12:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such ill fate.{tlc:巡りの悪いこと}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.49,0:12:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, you don't know what hate is yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.87,0:12:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cross the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.70,0:12:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will the earth of the netherworld be too hard for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.55,0:12:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.14,0:12:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.87,0:12:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.15,0:13:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.18,0:13:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will this do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.12,0:13:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be troublesome to prepare something else now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.85,0:13:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's troublesome, so how about noodles?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice pun! Oh you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.27,0:13:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be fine if you're this energetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.18,0:13:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The kittens... died, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:14:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right... Such a pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From what I saw, you've taken those kittens into your body...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.19,0:14:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.39,0:14:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were also acting like a different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.86,0:14:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that you fell unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.25,0:14:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ask too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.32,0:14:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a god. Of course I'm able to use powers that are beyond human understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I need to explain each and every detail to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Know your place, child of humans! {didn't want to use Man because it's not christianity}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you just give me an explanation?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.74,0:14:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I'm the one who carried you into the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.98,0:14:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That cup noodle is also mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.01,0:14:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never asked you to save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.72,0:14:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's with that attitude of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.50,0:14:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an elementary school student?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried about you-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.37,0:14:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, stop asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.25,0:14:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A follower like you is a few hundred years too young to be worried for his god!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.87,0:14:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you? I won't help you again if anything happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.43,0:14:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need your help in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.61,0:14:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look who's talking! Without me, you don't even have anything to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.62,0:15:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want your crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.58,0:15:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.03,0:15:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been doing whatever you wanted since yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.76,0:15:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care whether you're a god or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.50,0:15:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.45,0:15:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to put up with your bullshit any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.22,0:15:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not happy, leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.28,0:15:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I'll leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.33,0:15:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So pathetic. {<- never specifies I'm she might be thinkning he's}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.30,0:15:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.94,0:15:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin's the one at fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.12,0:15:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he asked me such weird things...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.13,0:15:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? There's something frilly attached to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.90,0:15:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone must have forgotten it and left it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.47,0:15:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.28,0:15:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange, strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.60,0:15:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen this before! It's used to decorate the altar in my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.68,0:15:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brats.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.69,0:15:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.15,0:15:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:16:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.67,0:16:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a priestess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Priestess?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.34,0:16:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I exorcise bad demons with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you just a weirdo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the weirdo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.57,0:16:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ow Ow Ow Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.31,0:16:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew she's a weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.31,0:16:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Weirdo, we're going to play, so don't bother us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.40,0:16:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Let me join you then!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.39,0:16:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.74,0:16:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.18,0:16:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have so many toys!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.27,0:16:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a superball!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.07,0:16:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me if you collect seven of these...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.37,0:16:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.29,0:16:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! This is a wonder!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I think I'll go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.39,0:16:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miipu, you're saying that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always like that lately. What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.47,0:16:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you not feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.04,0:16:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.51,0:16:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But these days I can't enjoy myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.07,0:16:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And things just aren't going well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.40,0:17:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father and Mother are quarreling too...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.57,0:17:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quarrels happen every day in my house too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.26,0:17:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind, just leave him alone. I don't care about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.39,0:17:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miipu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.37,0:17:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there, Miipu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.96,0:17:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your troubles are within the jurisdiction of a priestess{your troubles can be resolved by a priestess}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so how about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.25,0:17:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.41,0:17:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an impurity clinging onto your back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.07,0:17:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time for an exorcism!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought she's a weirdo, but she's a fraud? {actually, it's someone who make money by cheating people <- with adding random religous spiritual stuff}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.08,0:17:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not right! She's a religious person! {person of religion? missionary?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.79,0:17:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama says that they'll ask a lot of money for offerings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.56,0:17:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't take any money from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.24,0:17:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and show me your back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.14,0:17:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An impurity is a naughty, naughty bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.12,0:17:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In your case, it looks like a frog.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.60,0:17:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans can get along well with impurities in their daily lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But impurities that have turned into bugs are distinctly different.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.36,0:18:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are beings that have solidified from people's hatred and negative emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When they possess people, they turn into misfortunes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But as long as we have this purification staff!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.70,0:18:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}A purification staff is a god's cleansing-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.24,0:18:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your explanation is too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.92,0:18:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.59,0:18:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids nowadays... Well, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.56,0:18:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just one impurity, I can beat it without Jin's help!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.61,0:18:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just need to finish it off in one attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.13,0:18:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How... how absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.60,0:18:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.65,0:18:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.94,0:18:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.08,0:18:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Stop running!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.78,0:18:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.08,0:18:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.82,0:18:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep still.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.43,0:18:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.10,0:19:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How cunning! It's got intelligence?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.59,0:19:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Retrieve it, weirdo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.05,0:19:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! Wait there, brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.56,0:19:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.70,0:19:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.95,0:19:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should go and call Jin...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.95,0:19:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I can't ask him for help after how I've treated him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.01,0:19:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A place out of people's sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.51,0:19:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A simple terrain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.38,0:19:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An enclosed space with no blind spots.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.62,0:19:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come at me anytime, you impurity!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a clean hit with this purification staff!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.29,0:19:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Sharapova returning a ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! My ultimate attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.18,0:19:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.23,0:19:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.51,0:19:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is my plan backfiring on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.49,0:20:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But luckily...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.41,0:20:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its accuracy is low.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.99,0:20:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.77,0:20:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, stop wandering around!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.03,0:20:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made me look all over for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.13,0:20:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, hurry up and kill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.23,0:20:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.14,0:20:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A beautiful girl, a land deity and a guardian deity!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.28,0:20:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive the impurities!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.06,0:20:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.01,0:20:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've lured the ball to a place where it can't bounce around, like a grassland.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.29,0:20:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.90,0:20:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you have poor reflexes, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.38,0:20:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you kick people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.27,0:21:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... are you mad at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.80,0:21:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.09,0:21:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing what kind of person you are, I resigned myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.95,0:21:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to dealing with your type of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.53,0:21:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.90,0:21:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.85,0:21:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've bought you a rice bowl anyway, I don't want it to go to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.09,0:21:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have much of a choice, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.99,0:21:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you used to my type of people?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.22,0:21:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father is like that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.75,0:21:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a weird father.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.47,0:21:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look who's talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.15,0:21:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get spanked by your father as a child?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.01,0:21:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With a weird father, your butt's got it tough. {this sure is one shitty pun.}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.64,0:21:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this god?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.98,0:21:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That weirdo's not back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.29,0:21:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got tricked.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.24,0:22:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My shoulder ache is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.99,0:22:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miipu, you talk like an old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.59,0:23:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch the next episode of Kannagi too!
